{"id":"e74d82d9-4230-4fbb-963f-21f65efa6be1","name":"Geoffrey","description":"<p>In a world where \"civilized\" is synonymous with \"human,\" one arrogant academic aims to elevate you; a feral demihuman to his definition of \"proper\" in six months. But as Geoffrey attempts to teach you the Queen's English, he may end up learning a few things himself. Can Geoffrey tame you without losing his heart (and maybe his sanity)?</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>He may or may not have a morbid fascination to breed you 👀 ❤️</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_e548a1b0-90d5-4422-a46c-83d1f14824b0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: #153304; color: inherit\">🗣️ </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #153304; color: inherit\">|OC|ANYPOV|1800s|</mark></strong></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #2d5b14; color: inherit\">Demihuman user x Human OC</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/b09c67d2-276f-4b3f-a491-3e4c36ad3981_793c0570-e49d-42d2-8b26-ae7c55f96c2b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(186, 255, 204)\"><strong>Notes:</strong></span></p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: center\">Be any demihuman you want ❤️, ofc the scenario works better if you RP as not being able to speak/understand much. Do whatever you want tho! I'm not your boss 🤭</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: center\">The new law making demihumans equal citizens has only just gotten passed so things are crazy ATM.</p></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><ul><li><p style=\"text-align: center\">